d TCA — Transmission Channel Analysis for Stata
d Muhammad Alkhalaf (acad.helper88@gmail.com)
d
d Implements Transmission Channel Analysis (TCA) for structural
d vector autoregressive (SVAR) models following Wegner, Lieb, and
d Smeekes (2025, arXiv:2405.18987).
d
d Decomposes impulse response functions into transmission channel
d contributions using systems form representation and DAG path analysis.
